name: Intervarsity at FGCU
body:
### Intervarsity at FGCU

Welcome to Intervarsity at FGCU. We will be meeting on Fridays from 5-8pm, but haven't pinned down a room yet. This website will be up to date with the current room selection, so check back here if you'd like to come.


### Events

Coming up, there will be opportunities to travel to the Sonburst and Urbana conferences.
